OL,3,CArsonist leaves mother and children
OL,4,Chomeless after targeting wrong house
OL,6,FAn arsonist who set fire to an
OL,7,Finnocent family's home in an act of
OL,8,Fmisdirected revenge shortly after
OL,9,Fbeing released from prison has been
OL,10,Fjailed for five years.
OL,12,FPhillip Humphrey, 42, was sentenced at
OL,13,FManchester's Minshull Street Crown
OL,14,FCourt having previously pleaded guilty
OL,15,Fto charges of criminal damage and
OL,16,Farson, being reckless as to whether
OL,17,Flife would be endangered.
