OL,6,FThe court heard how Humphrey spent the
OL,7,Fafternoon drinking with friends in
OL,8,FRochdale town centre after being
OL,9,Freleased from prison, on Thursday, 16
OL,10,FNovember 2023.
OL,12,FAfter taking the party back to where
OL,13,Fhe was staying, he decided to target
OL,14,Fthe home of an innocent family on
OL,15,FOldham Road three times in one night,
OL,16,Fmistakenly believing the occupants had
OL,17,Fwronged him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
