OL,4,Chomeless after targeting wrong house
OL,6,FIn the early hours of Friday, 17
OL,7,FNovember, Humphrey smashed the windows
OL,8,Fof the house whilst the owner and her
OL,9,Fyoung children were inside.
OL,11,FPolice were called after the first
OL,12,Fincident, and the family made
OL,13,Farrangements to stay elsewhere as the
OL,14,Fincident had made them feel "extremely
OL,15,Funsafe", the court heard.
OL,17,FOn the second attempt Humphrey gained
OL,18,Faccess to the house, and on the third,
OL,19,Fset fire to the property, destroying
OL,20,Fthe family's clothes and sentimental
OL,21,Fbelongings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
