OL,6,FDetective Constable Russ Clarke, of
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police in Rochdale,
OL,8,Fsaid the family are now homeless after
OL,9,Fbeing forced to leave the property,
OL,10,Fwhich was rendered inhabitable.
OL,12,FHe said: "The family who lived at this
OL,13,Fproperty have lost everything they
OL,14,Fown, their clothes and all their
OL,15,Fbelongings, including items of
OL,16,Fsignificant sentimental value.
