OL,6,F"Humphrey evaded the police for over
OL,7,Ftwo months before finally being
OL,8,Farrested. During his interview,
OL,9,FHumphrey denied setting the fire and
OL,10,Fsought to implicate others, taking no
OL,11,Fresponsibility for his actions.
OL,13,F"It was only when further evidence was
OL,14,Fgathered that Humphrey accepted his
OL,15,Ffull involvement and pleaded guilty.
