OL,6,F"The impact on this family has been
OL,7,Fimmeasurable and this is clear within
OL,8,Fthe victim impact statement read out
OL,9,Fat court. They remain homeless and are
OL,10,Ffaced with rebuilding their lives once
OL,11,Fmore.
OL,13,F"I hope that the conviction of
OL,14,FHumphrey provides them with some level
OL,15,Fof comfort in what continues to be a
OL,16,Fvery difficult time for them."
